ider Easily Updated and Deployed a Scalable HIPAA Compliant Security System.\" A spokesman for Halifax confirmed Wednesday that it uses Verkada cameras but added that \"we believe the scope of the situation is limited.\"<p><div class=\"share_submission\" style=\"position:relative;\">
